CHANGELOG
================================================================================

* IStream, StreamReader, StringReader

  Added the method `Peek(int $bytes)` that will look ahead `$bytes` number of
  bytes and then reset the cursor to its previous position.

* File

  Added a method for truncating the file

* Logger

  Added the ability to truncate the logfile upon instantiation

* Feed

  Added a `FeedItem::GetLink()` method which gives the ability to get the first
  available link when multiple links exists (most likely in Atom feeds).

* Cache

  Added the method `Cache::Get2()` which will return the data even if the
  cache has expired.

